.content.about-aptible-hero
  .grid-container.grid--single-center.grid-item--adjacent
    %h2.about-aptible-hero__title.heading--single-center About Aptible
    %p.summary--single-center
      Security and compliance is more than data encryption and firewalls

  .grid-container--flex.about-aptible-hero__items
    .about-aptible-hero__item
      %h3.about-aptible-hero__subtitle Always Improving
      %p
        Aptible is constantly adding new functionality to help developers
        work safely with and protect the most meaningful, sensitive data in
        highly regulated industries.
      %p
        %a.arrow-link--right.dbl-arrow-link--right{ href: '/blog/' } Check out our newest features

    .about-aptible-hero__item
      %h3.about-aptible-hero__subtitle Developer Focused
      %p
        Aptible helps secure the internet by giving developers the tools and
        expertise to protect sensitive data. We provide clear and transparent
        documentation, a comprehensive CLI, integrations with popular developer
        tools, and a flexible and friendly UI.
      %p
        %a.arrow-link--right.dbl-arrow-link--right{ href: '/resources/' } Check out our documentation

    .about-aptible-hero__item
      %h3.about-aptible-hero__subtitle A Real Partner
      %p
        We provide enterprise-level support and guidance with your security and
        compliance challenges. Aptible has helped thousands of developers in
        some of the world's most innovative companies get up and running quickly
        and securely.
      %p
        %a.arrow-link--right.dbl-arrow-link--right{ href: '/support-plans/' } Learn how we can help your business
